      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single ASTM F1717 standardized configuration (44 mm offset, 10 deg angulation). Only one load condition evaluated; multi-angle or multi-offset testing not performed. Achieved level (2) falls below required level (3); this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized regulatory context of F1717."
