      "rationale": "Stiffness: E/uval = 1.21, difference = 4.3%. Yield force: E/uval = 0.87, difference = 2.9%. Force at 40 mm: E/uval = 1.44, difference = 6.1%. All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Experimental uncertainty uval computed from inter-laboratory variability and measurement system analysis."
